snippet.title: Gubbins Reveal Trailer (It's a word game) — Studio Folly
snippet.description:
We hope you like our game! Gubbins is a friendly puzzle game where you make words with the help and hindrance of silly little pals called Gubbins. It's kinda like solitaire x scrabble but with more friendly chaos.

Coming to planet Earth in 2023, starting with iOS.

FOLLOW ON TWITTER: https://twitter.com/folly_studio
WEBSITE: https://folly.studio
